Do children follow their parents' behaviour?&nbsp;&nbsp;🤔
&nbsp;
We placed eight children from different families in home settings and asked them to pretend to be mummy and daddy.
&nbsp;
Watch the video to see how the children picked up on traditional gender stereotypes and how their parents felt about it!
&nbsp;
What will your Gift to The Next Generation be?
